<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1051838' id='t-1051838'>All our memories are reconstructed memories.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1055478' id='t-1055478'>They are the product of what we originally experienced</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1057876' id='t-1057876'>and everything that's happened afterwards.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1060609' id='t-1060609'>They're dynamic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1062660' id='t-1062660'>They're malleable. They're volatile,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1065148' id='t-1065148'>and as a result, we all need to remember to be cautious,</span>
